STATE EX REL. KRONENBERG
v.
EIGHTH DIST. COURT OF APPEALS 2019-0094 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 10, 2019

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondents' motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DONNELLY, JJ., concur. STEWART, J., not participating.
